Drop downloadable files here (PDFs, CAD files, ZIPs, etc.).
Reference them in data/projects.js like:
  downloads: [
    { label: "Download PDF", file: "files/my-file.pdf" },
  ]

Put your resume here as:  files/resume.pdf
Then set  resumeFile: "files/resume.pdf"  in SITE.hero inside data/projects.js.

files/resume.pdf
